location.fullValue: Newbury II Plan, Westfields Single Family Homes

data.description: An absolute must see! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home has been meticulously maintained and is conveniently located in the highly sought after Westfields community! Built in 2018, this gem is loaded with upgrades that include pristine LVP flooring, granite countertops and granite center island, stainless steel appliances, beautifully painted interior walls, trendy light fixtures throughout, and quartz counters and modernized vanities in the bathrooms. All 4 upper level bedrooms are extremely spacious and boast a master suite with tray ceilings, dual walk in closets and dual vanities in the oversized en suite bathroom. Additional upgrades include an oversized garage with chic paint throughout, a fully fenced in VERY FLAT backyard that includes not only a trex deck off the kitchen but a full sized patio for all your summer cookout entertainment! The large partially finished basement has LVP flooring installed and is waiting for your finishing touches. This home is absolutley gorgeous, so schedule your showing today!
